\/p>\n  \n  <p><strong>Refunds:<\/strong> Issued only for defective or incorrect items, processed to the original payment method. For all other returns, store credit (valid 6 months) will be issued.<\/p>\n  \n  <p><strong>Non-Returnable Items:<\/strong> Sale items, customized\/altered products, worn\/damaged garments, accessories, and gift cards.<\/p>\n  \n  <h3>Return Process<\/h3>\n  <ul style=\"font-size:18px;\">\n    <li>Email <a href=\"mailto:ohkrabshop@ohkrab.com\">ohkrabshop@ohkrab.com<\/a> with your order ID and reason.<\/li>\n    <li>Customers must ship the product back at their own cost (flat INR 200 return fee).<\/li>\n    <li>Address: Oh Krab!, Plot No 17, Sector 7, IMT Manesar, Gurgaon, Haryana – 122050.<\/li>\n  <\/ul>\n  \n  <p><strong>Defective\/Incorrect Items:<\/strong> Report within 48 hours with order ID, issue description, and an unboxing video. Verified cases are eligible for exchange or refund.<\/p>\n  \n  <p><strong>Processing Time:<\/strong> 7–10 business days after the item passes quality check. Confirmation of store credit\/refund will follow via email.<\/p>\n  \n  <h2>Shipping & Delivery<\/h2>\n  \n  <p><strong>Order Processing:<\/strong> 4–5 business days after confirmation.<\/p>\n  \n  <h3>Delivery Timelines<\/h3>\n  <ul style=\"font-size:18px;\">\n    <li>Metro (India): 3–5 business days after dispatch<\/li>\n    <li>Non-metro: 5–8 business days after dispatch<\/li>\n    <li>International (Excluding UAE): ~14 business days (customs duties borne by customer)<\/li>\n<li>UAE: 7-10 business days after dispatch<\/li>\n  <\/ul>\n  \n  <p><strong>Express Shipping:<\/strong> Priority shipping (1–3 days) available in India for INR 400 (not available on COD).<\/p>\n  \n  <h3>Shipping Charges<\/h3>\n  <ul style=\"font-size:18px;\">\n    <li>India: Free on prepaid orders and orders above ₹3000<\/li>\n    <li>COD: Available <\/li>\n    <li>International: Calculated at Checkout<\/li>\n  <\/ul>\n  \n  <p><strong>Tracking:<\/strong> Real-time tracking via SMS, WhatsApp, and email updates from Shipway.<\/p>\n  \n  <p><strong>Delivery Notes:<\/strong> Timelines may vary due to holidays or unforeseen delays. Orders with incorrect details will be reshipped at customer’s cost. Special gift\/hold requests can be sent to <a href=\"mailto:ohkrabshop@ohkrab.com\">ohkrabshop@ohkrab.com<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/section>"}},"faq_4H8pQ8":{"type":"faq","settings":{"title":"FAQ's","qcl":"#333333","qfs":13,"qfsm":13,"qfw":"600","bdr":"#dddddd"}}},"block_order":["descriptions","spec_eyp8Bk","review","0ffa6649-39c4-4d0d-a030-0b83e8ea10b2","ca4b9cc3-1de5-4957-9152-20d832cd0b41","faq_4H8pQ8"],"custom_css":["p {font-size: 15px;}"],"settings":{"section_width":false,"tab_style":"1","tab_align":"left","tfs":15,"tff":"ft2","tfw":"600","cl":"#111111","tbg":"#f5f5f5","bdr":"#dddddd","cla":"#111111","tbga":"#ffffff","bdra":"#dddddd","bbrd":0,"clm":"#000000","tbgm":"#eeeeee","bdrm":"#ffffff","clam":"#eeeeee","tbgam":"#000000","bdram":"#eeeeee"}},"175818346184f8a404":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"judge_me_reviews_review_widget_TbkNfG":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/judge-me-reviews\/blocks\/review_widget\/61ccd3b1-a9f2-4160-9fe9-4fec8413e5d8","settings":{"review_data":"sample_data","max_width":1200,"show_shop_reviews":false,"empty_state":"empty_widget"}}},"block_order":["judge_me_reviews_review_widget_TbkNfG"],"settings":{"top-offeset":"default","section_width":true,"npd":false,"section_cov":false,"sec_bg_clr":"#fafafa"}},"related-products":{"type":"related-products","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"Related Products","subtitle":"","section_width":false,"type":"1","grid":4,"tablet-grid":3,"mobile-grid":2,"row":"5","autoplay":true,"speed":5}},"175810847541e4cf28":{"type":"apps","settings":{"top-offeset":"default","section_width":true,"npd":false,"section_cov":false,"sec_bg_clr":"#fafafa"}},"recommendations":{"type":"product-recommendations","custom_css":[".gridSwatches {display: none;}"],"settings":{"title":"RECOMMENDED PRODUCTS","subtitle":"","section_widt